folder: Union Square (West) & 16th Street & Broadway & [Union Square Park.], Manhattan, NY
text:
(1)
Union Square West, north from but not including 16th Street (east), to and including Broadway. Also seen is Broadway, east side, north from but not including 17th Street (east). A section of Union Square Park is seen in the foreground.
May, 1924.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, from a different angle.
June, 1924.

P. L. Sperr.
title: Manhattan: Union Square (West) - 16th Street - Broadway - [Union Square Park.]
